    <section id="introduction">
      <div class="container">
          <h3 class="pb-2">Learn language in a new way.</h3>
          <p>Hi! We’re TVSensei (<em>tee-vee-sen-say-ee</em>).</p>
          <p>We’re out to <strong>revolutionize</strong> language learning as we know it!</p>
          <p>TVSensei teaches users to speak foreign languages in the context seen on screen—engaging learners with popular TV shows as both audience and actor using <strong>lessons designed by us</strong>.</p>
          <p>Scroll down to learn about our mission and our product. And if you're interested, <a href="#">Sign up</a> to see our wonderful contents!</p>
      </div>
